---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Thesis
description: Our investment philosophy and approach to backing technical founders at the frontier.
permalink: /thesis/
---

<section class="py-16 sm:py-20">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400 mb-6">Investment Thesis</p>
      <h1 class="font-sans font-light tracking-tighter text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl max-w-3xl text-gray-900" style="line-height: 0.95;">
        What we look for
      </h1>
    </div>

    <!-- Traits -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-16">
      <div class="p-5 rounded-xl border border-black/10 bg-gray-50">
        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900">Obsessed founders</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
          With a deeply personal motivation to succeed — founders who can't not build this.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-5 rounded-xl border border-black/10 bg-gray-50">
        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900">Big swings</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
          We don't do incremental. We back founders going after transformative outcomes.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-5 rounded-xl border border-black/10 bg-gray-50">
        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900">Clear view</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
          On the pathway to success — the ability to see the whole field at a glance (<em>coup d'œil</em>).
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-5 rounded-xl border border-black/10 bg-gray-50">
        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900">Competitive advantage</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
          Convincing logic for achieving sustained differentiation that compounds over time.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-5 rounded-xl border border-black/10 bg-gray-50">
        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900">Interested in help</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
          If it improves odds of success. We're active partners, not passive capital.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-5 rounded-xl border border-black/10 bg-gray-50">
        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900">Kindness</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
          Founders and teams must be kind at heart. Life is too short for anything else.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Sectors -->
    <div class="mb-16">
      <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400 mb-6">Focus Sectors</p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-3">
        {% for sector in site.sectors %}
        {% if not sector.deemphasized %}
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl text-center transition-all hover:scale-105" style="background: {{ sector.color }}15; border: 1px solid {{ sector.color }}30;">
          <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full mx-auto mb-2" style="background-color: {{ sector.color }};"></div>
          <span class="text-sm font-medium" style="color: {{ sector.color }};">{{ sector.name }}</span>
        </div>
        {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Stage & Check Size -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 pt-8 border-t border-black/10">
      <div>
        <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400 mb-2">Stage</p>
        <p class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Pre-Seed · Seed</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400 mb-2">Check Size</p>
        <p class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">$10K – $100K</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
